{"tid":1437406,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［入黎傾下］六度分隔理論","createTime":"2019-08-09T13:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T07:03:50.000Z","uid":66700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1e6e0a89636b408fc72fa062bcba0011833add","tid":1437406,"uid":66700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:50:34.000Z","msg":"依家tg好多大谷都會有好多唔認識既同路人喺度一齊同行，為緊我地既香港出一分力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係同時都會有大量既<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">情報犬</span></span></strong>喺度收料。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左阻擋<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">情報犬</span></span></strong>，我地係咪應該都喺網絡/通訊上都保護自己同其他人呢？<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n六度分隔理論（英語：Six Degrees of Separation）認為世界上任何互不相識的兩人，只需要很少的中間人就能夠建立起聯繫。哈佛大學心理學教授斯坦利&middot;米爾格拉姆於1967年根據這個概念做過一次連鎖信實驗，嘗試證明平均只需要6步就可以聯繫任何兩個互不相識的美國人。<br />\n//<br />\nFrom Wikipedia<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢個實驗最初係用喺唔相識既陌生人，但係呢個理論相反我地可以應用喺相識既朋友度。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">四海之內皆兄弟</span></span></strong><br />\n縱使我地各人行動可能不一致，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">只要理念相同</span></span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">核爆都唔割</span></span></strong>既時候，而我地身邊有三兩個 / 四五個呢啲既朋友，佢地身邊又會有相類同既朋友。一變四 四變十二，相信可以達到一個理想既人數一齊參與呢場運動。<br />\n<br />\n加上呢場運動需要既係信念夠堅定，行動夠一致。<br />\n我地可以以呢個方向，喺tg以朋友搭朋友咁開谷交流一齊各有各做。再每個大谷都有溝通，情報就可以只流於內部。<br />\n<br />\n當然，要講個「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">信</span></span></strong>」字，even喺朋友谷入面唔識既朋友，咁先可以進一步鞏固「不割蓆、不篤灰、不分化」呢個原則。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而喺呢一場咁持久既運動入面，我地又能唔能夠利用呢個理論去阻隔一啲所謂「滲透」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知我講到1999，但都希望可以討論下個可行性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MdHfi0M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdHfi0M.png&h=2f7f2e85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6aef8f9c0a276e65a8b3157f16f7b50d1fa89736","tid":1437406,"uid":66700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:52:18.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42c0e433a0a50d60047a851a44ea919d89634d5","tid":1437406,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"呢個理論好似算係落後🤔<br />\n家陣通訊方便咗咁多 應該再快啲"},{"pid":"77cad4514ce487a23459cc243e615edc67b69cc7","tid":1437406,"uid":66700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c42c0e433a0a50d60047a851a44ea919d89634d5","tid":1437406,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"呢個理論好似算係落後🤔<br />\n家陣通訊方便咗咁多 應該再快啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"係既 但依家咁多流料同情報犬<br />\n大谷討論啲乜都會俾全世界知<br />\n雖然方便 但都可以好容易被混淆視聽<br />\n朋友搭朋友起碼個心都定啲先"},{"pid":"b4f35eb805f0946ffa842ac31984e593a6ac4c42","tid":1437406,"uid":66700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:03:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87350e090c193b34bce19ff151e87eb2ea970fab","tid":1437406,"uid":66700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:03:50.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"}]}